  "description":  "Genoa golden curve fixtures — locked to the vendored FCC contours-api-node tvfm_curves.js (F(50,50) and F(50,10)) and gwave.js (AM groundwave).  Each expected value was computed by directly invoking the vendored FCC routines (fcc.tvfmfs_metric / fcc.amDistanceKm) against the pinned 25 × 13 tabulations and the AM groundwave field grid.  PASS proves Genoa's engine produces FCC-canonical output for FM service contour, FM interfering contour (§74.1204), and AM groundwave (§73.183 / §73.184).",
